        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size:22px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500;">India-China Border Deal</h2>
        </mj-text>
         <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopolitics.world/email/images/gp-oct-23-1.jpg" alt="India-China Border Deal" href="https://www.geopolitics.world" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">India and China have reached an agreement on patrolling arrangements along their <a href="https://apnews.com/article/india-china-ladakh-border-standoff-c7c5fcf61b2378428842207b52b547c3" target="_blank">disputed Himalayan border</a>, following talks to reduce tensions that escalated into <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-54067400" target="_blank">deadly clashes</a> in 2020. The agreement aims to ensure disengagement and resolve ongoing issues at the Line of Actual Control, which separates their territories. Read more about the India-China dispute <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53062484" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">While specifics of the arrangement remain unclear, it is seen as a step towards easing strained relations between the two nations ahead of India‚Äôs Prime Minister Modi‚Äôs upcoming visit to Russia for the <a href="https://www.geopolitics.world/archives/brics-summit-moldova-votes-yes-israel-documents-leaked" target="_blank">BRICS summit</a>. The relationship between China and India is complex aside from the territorial disputes, as both are major rival powers in Asia. However, this has not always been the case (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yeXzB53Xu08" target="_blank">watch video</a>). Relations between China and India started warm in the 1950s after the foundation of Modern China and India‚Äôs independence.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
